  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="feature-with-icon">
          <div class="icon"><%= image_tag "icons/cash.png" %></div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Your money, your way</h3>
            <em><small>Collect money using cash, check, PayPal, WePay, or Dwolla</small></em>
          </div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="feature-with-icon">
          <div class="icon"><%= image_tag "icons/group.png" %></div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Don't be the bad guy</h3>
            <em><small>Social accountability puts peer pressure on group members</small></em>
          </div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="feature-with-icon second-row">
          <div class="icon"><%= image_tag "icons/thumbs.png" %></div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Enjoy the event</h3>
            <em><small>Easier payment collection makes the event easier to enjoy</small></em>
          </div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <div class="feature-with-icon second-row">
          <div class="icon"><%= image_tag "icons/ledger.png" %></div>
          <div class="feature">
            <h3>Stay on top of things</h3>
            <em><small>Keep track of who has paid and track progress</small></em>
          </div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row row-split push-bottom">
    <div class="span5 static-width">
      <%= image_tag "nudge_demo.png", class: 'img-polaroid' %>
    </div>
    <div class="span7 home-feature-description">
      <h3>Let group members remind each other</h3>
      <em><small>Our nudge feature lets users who have already paid put the pressure on the unpaid users. In many group payment situations, the whole group benefits from everyone paying. There's no reason why the event organizer should be the only one that reminds people to pay. Nudging will help you get your money!</small></em>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span12">
      <h2>Coming soon:</h2>

      <h3>Split the Bill</h3>
      <em><small>Ever have the annoying issue of splitting a restaurant bill? Our next roll out will include an easy to use – split the receipt process that makes it simple to split a bill according to what each person ordered.</small></em>

      <h3 class="push-top-small">Contractual Agreements</h3>
      <em><small>Rent, weekend getaways, club dues etc. can get very pricey. Organizers in these cases would obviously like some legally binding documentation that proves each person in the group owes them a certain amount. Our upcoming contractual agreement option will allow organizers to request such legally binding terms to be placed upon their group members. A bit of further reassurance can never hurt!</small></em>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

